---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog
description: Updates, deep dives, and release notes from the Tuist team.
permalink: /blog/
---

<section class="blog-index">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Blog</p>
    <h1>Notes from the Tuist team.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Release notes, OTP patterns, and lessons we learn while building production AI agents on the BEAM.</p>
    <p class="blog-feeds">Subscribe via <a href="/blog/rss.xml">RSS</a> or <a href="/blog/feed.xml">Atom</a>.</p>
    {% set posts = collections.posts | reverse %}
    {% if posts.length == 0 %}
      <p class="muted">No posts yet.</p>
    {% else %}
      <ol class="post-list" reversed>
      {% for post in posts %}
        <li>
          <a href="{{ post.url }}">
            <p class="post-list-date">
              <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
            </p>
            <h2>{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
            {% if post.data.description %}<p class="post-list-desc">{{ post.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
      </ol>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
